Actually I found a solution:
In preamble I put
\newenvironment{pseudoequation}[1][]{\refstepcounter{equation}}{}
-- 

and instead of the above I write

\begin{pseudoequation}\label{myequation}\end{pseudoequation}
\begin{equation}
x_\pm = a \pm b
\tag*{$(\theequation)_\pm$}
\label{myequationpm}
\end{equation}

Then \ref{myequationpm} returns $(6.4)_\pm$ but 
$(\ref{myequation})_+$ returns $(6.4)_+$
and this works fine with hyperref package as well

